# Camera Visual Interface - Cockpit_Drone Wiki (English 
Summary)

The `camera.pas` unit defines the visual form `TfrmCam` responsible for displaying images or graphical data related to the 
drone's camera. It includes a custom grid component (`gridCam`), an image display component (`Image1`), and labels for textual 
information. The unit currently lacks functional code, serving as a visual container for future implementation of camera-related 
features such as video streaming or image processing.

